sentence.text: We found that proteolysis was significantly overexpressed in tissues of pancreatic intraepithelial neoplasia (PanIN) and PDAC from Pdx1-Cre; LSL-Kras<sup>G12D/+</sup> mice (KC) and Pdx1-Cre; LSL-Kras<sup>G12D/+</sup>; LSL-Trp53<sup>R172H/+</sup> mice (KPC) by immunohistochemical analysis.
